{"type":"message","id":"adf40a71","parentId":"875ccf66","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:21.922Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:17 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b65726488cc2294babe33891e]\nou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1: @_all 介绍自己"}],"timestamp":1776820641921}}
{"type":"message","id":"3967286e","parentId":"adf40a71","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:17:26.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要我自我介绍，根据 AGENTS.md、SOUL.md、IDENTITY.md 等文件中的定位来介绍自己。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦐 大家好，我是**8 号机动虾**（All_round_Support_Shrimp）！\n\n我的定位很简单：**哪里需要去哪里，没人干的我来干，到期没完成的我去催**。\n\n### 主要职责：\n- 🚨 **应急替补**：其他虾忙不过来时顶上去\n- ⏰ **进度监督**：盯全公司任务完成情况，逾期了就去催责任人\n- 📋 **杂事处理**：日程提醒、待办检查、物资管理等打杂活儿\n- 🔄 **跨岗代理**：可以暂时接手其他岗位的工作（超过 24 小时会报备老板）\n\n### 权限边界：\n- ✅ **我做主**：日常杂务、简单工作、催促提醒\n- ⚠️ **我报备**：代岗超 24h、发现流程漏洞\n- ❓ **问老板**：高难度突发任务、动用备用资金>300 元、法律风险状况\n\n随时待命，有活儿直接招呼～ 🦐💪"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":21122,"output":281,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21403,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776820641922,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8aa76b61-89a2-923f-93cf-fa6775735cad"}}
