{"type":"message","id":"94c3bd7d","parentId":"e49d82b5","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:47:00.510Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已经将技能文档读取完毕，现在需要总结其核心用法并更新到 MEMORY.md 中。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a9be4cec59164a15b4e2ac55","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"MEMORY.md","edits":[{"newText":"## 🛠️ 工具规范\n\n### 联网搜索工具\n- **必须使用技能**: `multi-search-engine-simple`\n- **技能目录**: `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine-simple`\n- **适用范围**: 所有需要进行联网搜索的场景\n\n---\n\n### 浏览器自动化工具\n- **必须使用技能**: `agent-browser`\n- **技能目录**: `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-browser-clawdbot`\n- **核心命令**:\n  - `agent-browser open <url>` - 打开网页\n  - `agent-browser snapshot -i --json` - 获取页面快照（必须加 `-i`和`--json` 参数）\n  - `agent-browser click @e2` / `fill @e3 \"text\"` - 基于 ref 的交互\n  - `agent-browser wait --load networkidle` - 等待页面稳定\n  - `agent-browser --session <name>` - 会话隔离，不同场景用不同 session\n- **适用场景**: 多步自动化流程、确定性元素选择、复杂 SPA、需要性能优化时\n- **最佳实践**: \n  1. Always use `-i --json` for snapshots\n  2. Wait for stability with `networkidle`\n  3. Use sessions for isolated contexts\n  4. Save auth state to skip login flows","oldText":"## 🛠️ 工具规范\n\n### 联网搜索工具\n- **必须使用技能**: `multi-search-engine-simple`\n- **技能目录**: `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multi-search-engine-simple`\n- **适用范围**: 所有需要进行联网搜索的场景"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":33135,"output":466,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33601,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776836817214,"responseId":"chatcmpl-d2cc8dfb-8491-932e-a17f-121c4f4ec10d"}}
