{"type":"message","id":"e04010e5","parentId":"f1e2d7ab","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:47:02.984Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"工具调用成功，需要向用户汇报已总结的技能要点和核心用法。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已学习并保存到记忆！\n\n## 🧠 agent-browser 技能总结\n\n**是什么**: 面向 AI 代理的无头浏览器自动化工具，基于 accessibility tree snapshot 实现确定性元素选择\n\n**核心命令流**:\n```bash\n1. agent-browser open <url>          # 打开网页\n2. agent-browser snapshot -i --json   # 获取快照（必须加这两个参数）\n3. agent-browser click @e2 / fill @e3 \"text\"  # 基于 ref 交互\n4. agent-browser wait --load networkidle # 等页面稳定\n5. agent-browser screenshot/pdf page.*  # 截图或生成 PDF\n```\n\n**关键特性**:\n- ✅ Ref-based selection (如 `@e2`) - 确定性交互\n- ✅ Session isolation (`--session admin/user`) - 隔离上下文\n- ✅ State persistence (`state save/load`) - 跳过登录流程\n- ✅ Network control - 路由、mock、拦截广告\n- ✅ Multi-tab support - 多标签页管理\n\n**适用场景**: 多步自动化工作流、复杂 SPA 应用、需要确定性和性能的场景\n\n已记录到 MEMORY.md~🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":33606,"output":291,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33897,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776836820535,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8ea56ba5-07b4-9fbf-98a6-c7420041f0b6"}}
