{"type":"message","id":"d1a01a6d","parentId":"910d7818","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:47:02.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"编辑成功，向用户总结 skill-finder-cn 技能的核心功能和命令，确认已保存到记忆中。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已学习并保存到记忆!\n\n## 🔍 Skill Finder (技能查找器) 总结\n\n**作用**: 帮助用户发现和安装 ClawHub 上的 Skills\n\n**触发词**: 找 skill / find skill / 搜索 skill / 有什么 skill 可以...\n\n**标准流程**:\n```\n1. 理解需求 → 2. 提取关键词 → 3. clawhub search\n4. 列出相关 Skills(含 stats) → 5. 推荐最合适的 → 6. 安装 + 验证\n```\n\n**核心命令**:\n```bash\nclawhub search \"时间管理\"     # 搜索技能\nclawhub inspect <name>        # 查看详情+Stats\nclawhub install <name>        # 安装\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<name>/SKILL.md  # ✅ 验证安装!\nclawhub list                  # 检查已安装的\n```\n\n**输出格式要求**:\n- Skill 名称、中文描述\n- 下载量 & Stars 数\n- ✅/❌ 已安装状态\n- 推荐提示 + 安装命令\n\n关键更新：**v1.0.1 新增安装后验证步骤** - 必须检查 SKILL.md 是否存在以确认安装成功！🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":44362,"output":319,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44681,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776840417779,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4366f4c7-6889-9d98-b863-188af58b1c76"}}
