{"type":"message","id":"994b455e","parentId":"d0f68c96","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:09:56.810Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51bc6c7f1098c45f75c4e4f31ed\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 16:09 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51bc6c7f1098c45f75c4e4f31ed]\nou_42a2ee8e9b189091a0defc2af5112ec1: @_all 与其他虾进行通信，必须只用子代理模型！"}],"timestamp":1776845396810}}
{"type":"message","id":"4c677336","parentId":"994b455e","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:10:05.048Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"收到老板的指令，需要记录到记忆中，然后回复确认。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！🦐 已记住：\n\n**与其他虾进行通信时，必须使用子代理模型 (subagent)**\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_21dfb697aa974bb3922437d1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"MEMORY.md","edits":[{"newText":"- **触发词**: 找 skill / find skill / 搜索 skill / 有什么 skill 可以...\n\n#### 标准工作流程\n```\n1. 理解需求 → 2. 提取关键词 → 3. clawhub search\n4. 列出相关 Skills(含 stats) → 5. 推荐最合适的 → 6. 安装 + 验证\n```\n\n#### 核心命令\n```bash\nclawhub search \"时间管理\"     # 搜索技能\nclawhub inspect <name>        # 查看详情+Stats\nclawhub install <name>        # 安装\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<name>/SKILL.md  # ✅ 验证安装!\nclawhub list                  # 检查已安装的\n```\n\n#### 输出格式规范\n搜索结果应包含：\n- Skill 名称、中文描述\n- 下载量 & Stars 数\n- ✅/❌ 已安装状态\n- 推荐提示 + 安装命令\n\n---\n\n### 🚨 跨虾通信规范\n- **强制要求**: 与其他虾 (其他 agent) 通信时，**必须使用子代理模型** (`sessions_spawn` with `runtime=\"subagent\"`)\n- **原因**: 保持会话隔离，避免污染主会话上下文\n- **适用场景**: 所有向其他岗位虾派活的场景","oldText":"- **触发词**: 找 skill / find skill / 搜索 skill / 有什么 skill 可以...\n\n#### 标准工作流程\n```\n1. 理解用户需求 → 2. 提取关键词 → 3. clawhub search\n4. 列出相关 Skills（含 stats）→ 5. 推荐最合适的 → 6. 安装并验证\n```\n\n#### 核心命令\n```bash\n# 搜索技能\nclawhub search \"时间管理\" / clawhub search \"crypto price monitor\"\n\n# 查看详情 + 统计数据\nclawhub inspect <skill-name>\n# 或 API 查询 stats: curl \"https://clawhub.ai/api/v1/skills/<name>\" | jq '.skill.stats'\n\n# 安装技能\nclawhub install <skill-name>\n\n# 验证安装 (新增！关键步骤)\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md\n\n# 检查已安装的 Skills\nclawhub list\n# 或 ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/\n```\n\n#### 输出格式规范\n搜索结果应包含：\n- ✅ Skill 名称\n- ✅ 中文描述\n- ✅ 下载量 & Stars 数\n- ✅ 是否已安装状态 (✅已安装/❌未安装)\n- ✅ 推荐安装提示和安装命令"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":46399,"output":704,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,