{"type":"message","id":"48655e70","parentId":"e2223469","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:10:08.013Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d88678a4d0524146bad9d4f7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n### Skill Finder (技能查找器)\n- **技能目录**: `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-finder-cn`\n- **触发词**: 找 skill、find skill、搜索 skill、有什么 skill 可以...\n- **作用**: 帮助用户发现和安装 ClawHub 上的 Skills\n\n#### 标准工作流程\n```\n1. 理解用户需求 → 2. 提取关键词 → 3. clawhub search \"关键词\"\n4. 列出相关 Skills(含 stats) → 5. 推荐最合适的 → 6. 安装并验证\n```\n\n#### 核心命令\n```bash\n# 搜索技能\nclawhub search \"时间管理\" / clawhub search \"crypto price monitor\"\n\n# 查看详情+统计数据\nclawhub inspect <skill-name>\n\n[21 more lines in file. Use offset=213 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776845408012}}
