{"type":"message","id":"770a27ed","parentId":"9af74474","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:10:43.240Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已更新记忆文件，现在需要向用户确认这项跨虾通信规范已记录完成。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已记录！🦐\n\n**跨虾通信强制规则**:\n- 🚫 **禁止**: 直接用主会话与其他虾通信\n- ✅ **必须**: 使用 `sessions_spawn(runtime=\"subagent\")` 子代理模式\n- 💡 **原因**: 保持会话隔离，避免污染主上下文\n\n以后派活给其他岗位虾时会自动用子代理！💪"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":51843,"output":127,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51970,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776845441140,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e390e457-1f83-9d4e-a598-0d6fa247c625"}}
